<recipe lang="en-uk" xmlns:lxslt="http://xml.apache.org/xslt">
<title><![CDATA[Chana Dal with Zucchini or Bottle Gourd]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[Louki Chana Dal. Can also be done with yellow split peas]]></description>
<source/>
<img></img>
<cuisine>
<style>Indian</style>
<region>Uttar Pradesh</region>
<approach/>
</cuisine>
<tags>
<tag>Dal</tag>
<tag/>
</tags>
<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Soak dal 5 hours, then drain.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add water and bring to boil over high heat, skimming. Cook for 10 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Lower heat and add ginger, coriander, turmeric, ghee, and cook on low heat for 1.5 hrs with a tight fitting lid]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Away from fire add gourd and garam masala, then cook for another 30 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[When gourd is butter soft add lemon juice and salt to taste]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[In a small pan fry chilies and cumin seeds. When browned add assafoetida and curry leaves. A few seconds later drop into the dal.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Let stand a couple of minutes, covered, then serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
